hyprland (0.44.1-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.44.1
  * 4520b30d version: bump to 0.44.1
  * 8405aa11 output: update state even if no owner exists (#8044)
  * ad46257c output/xdg-output: avoid sending events to released globals
  * 0cfbe618 keyboard: update group state on change for the sym resolve
    state
  * 7d0944ac defaultConfig: add a nofocus rule for weird X windows
  * b9990468 pointer: expand sw cursor damage box
  * 736a8735 keybinds: fixup xkb_states for resolve_by_sym
  * b54eecbd config: give simple help for super+q not working
  * 657aeb39 screencopy: fix screencopy frames not being cleaned up
    (#8017)
  * 6807430b layout: fix auto group when opening a new window in a non-
    focused workspace using window rules (#8006)

 -- Constantin Piber <cp.piber@gmail.com>  Wed, 09 Oct 2024 18:17:51 +0200

hyprland (0.44.0-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.44.0
  * 0c7a7e2d version: bump to 0.44.0
  * 0ec6072a single-pixel: set buffer size to 1,1
  * 3ca699de opengl: use GL_CLAMP_TO_EDGE instead of GL_CLAMP
  * 52c09196 monitor: arrange monitors on connect and disconnect
  * 6fbfeefc protocolmgr: don't expose the fallback output
  * 46bf87c8 monitor: use a scope guard for disconnect events
  * 595eb89f renderer: Fix resize artifacts (stretching, bumps) (#7499)
  * a815b14b monitor: cleanup and modernize scheduleDone
  * 3a5052a7 compositor: update all xdg outputs on arrange
  * 8e237b00 xdg-output: minor cleanups
  * 1ed925b6 internal: fix missing include directive (#7984)
  * aed529f6 renderer: fix uvBR calculation (#7975)
  * de68e065 layout: fix dragging a window into a group after e242694
    (#7976)
  * e2426942 layout: add auto_group to control default grouping (#7883)
  * 5c6c300a wayland/output: send geometry in updateState
  * 6bd33971 wlr-output-management: accept 0 refresh rates
  * 68fd32c8 byteoperations: add missing header
  * 3ddb16bd compositor/wayland: up the max buffer size to avoid
    disconnects when app hangs
  * f6387536 protocol: fix missing include
  * 968f6a60 meson: fix arch build with new protocol
  * 488efab6 single-pixel-buffer: new protocol impl
  * 6649255d flake.lock: update
  * 4b00cba3 dwindle: add movetoroot method to layout messages (#7903)
  * 9e418671 config: add descriptions for dwindle and master layout
    options (#7933)
  * d73c1475 CI/Nix: git+https -> github
  * 6f313de9 core: Fix Musl builds (#7934)
  * 2cf6e786 dwindle: add config option `split_bias` (#7920)
  * 58669fef flake.lock: update
  * e20aef7d opengl: remove debug log
  * b2143a98 CI/Nix: no longer build with submodules
  * f75f8efb Meson: add tracy dependency
  * be96787e CMake: use udis86 from pkg-config, fallback to subproject
  * 89d945aa CMake: use hyprland-protocols from pkg-config, fallback to
    subproject
  * 27211c71 Meson: try to find udis86 through pkgconfig, fallback to
    subproject
  * 14942bca Nix: re-add hyprland-protocols
  * 77f2a013 flake.lock: update nixpkgs
  * 7b56ce65 CI/Nix: add cross build
  * 32a8caf7 Nix: also test cross build
  * caaa9b11 wlr-output-configuration: Improve output configuration
    (#7571)
  * b1ad2d80 dispatchers: fixup dpms toggle (#7875)
  * 22746b30 hyprctl: use the getMonitorData helper everywhere
  * 49713fab pointermgr: avoid hogging CMonitor refs
  * 8b86ee8b github: encourage usage of --systeminfo if Hyprland won't
    launch
  * 2a052c69 core: add a --systeminfo parameter to gather systeminfo
    without running
  * 2320b224 Internal: move to Mat3x3 from hyprutils (#7902)
  * 8f518826 hyprctl: add solitary field to hyprctl monitors
  * 00c86268 hyprctl: add submap request
  * 0a211f29 hyprctl: add defaultName to workspacerules
  * d279d7c4 eventloop: dispatch pending in session on start
  * 6c78b03b flake: update xdph
  * f7949708 internal: nuke wlsignal and related
  * 508bde1f core: add HYPRLAND_CONFIG environment variable (#7851)
  * e5ff19ac flake: update xdph
  * 8579066c Nix: clean up derivation
  * 9232bc2c internal: move to hyprutils' scopeguard
  * db0b764a shm: send a static list of shm formats
  * 278583b8 flake.lock: update
  * 4414cd07 xwm: Minor cleanup, add wrappers for basic types (#7856)
  * 9e98fb01 dmabuffer: attempt importing failed dmabufs as implicit
  * 98563783 Nix: use mold linker
  * dfa1bd0c Meson: pass AQUAMARINE_VERSION argument
  * 92df6b0d version: log build aquamarine version
  * 71963972 args: add --version to binary args
  * 1bc05b1f xwayland: use proper path for the XWayland sockets (#7852)
  * e6cf643f pointermgr: Hide hardware cursor on leave (#7806)
  * 94140e88 xwayland: Some readability improvements (#7807)
  * b248d597 Nix: fix meson PCH flag
  * cbc0ff6e Nix: disable PCH
  * 6b6554ad flake.nix: inherit stdenv from package
  * d936eb43 flake.lock: update aquamarine
  * 883d0108 userchecks: add an xdg_current_desktop check
  * 0564b46a dispatchers: allow moveintogroup when floating (#7818)
  * 3c9716ac gammactrl: fix potential crash on monitor removed (#7828)
  * 581f6659 data-device: conform to reported source actions
  * e72ae6b2 hyprctl: allow parsing empty value
  * 9e356562 internal: Delay monitor events/hooks (#7797)
  * e8775852 internal: Fix change group current fullscreen state query
    (#7802)
  * eb97d949 textinput: don't reset if ti isn't enabled (#7798)
  * e74efd87 internal: fix initial cursor warping (#7793)
  * 4dbdb556 data-device: don't send default action of move
  * 5ee4b196 data-device: send clock time in motion events
  * d35e70a8 cmake: drop ninja dep
  * c35ed836 nix: adapt cmake options
  * d505b336 nix: use meson
  * 118be4de textinput: fix tiv3 leave (#7761)
  * 73b9756b xwayland: remove extra x11 deactivation (#7755)
  * 8b9e3859 [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * e01da1fd Meson: format
  * 7a8c013e Meson: fix protocols, clean up
  * 518399a9 pointermgr: avoid derefing null outputs
  * 155d4401 textinput: handle IME resetting (#7731)
  * 13f90bb8 update xdph commit in flake.lock
  * c67b257e build: Set cmake_minimum_required to version 3.30 (#7709)
  * 8237d7e1 input: move dmps activation to input listeners (#7721)
  * 85da1a17 [gha] build man pages
  * 9609b04f man: Fixed the man page to show the new information (#7713)
  * 04421063 config: add order rule for layers (#7697)
  * 43e1415e assets: Remove execute permission from lockdead.png (#7715)
