hyprland (0.43.0-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.43.0
  * 0f594732 props: bump version to 0.43.0
  * 312411fc windows: support size with pseudo tiled
  * 70add904 config: add exec-shutdown for running commands on shutdown
    (#7683)
  * 5ca48231 config: Added default button mapping for xf86 keys (#7672)
  * 05002130 input: try to refocus a focusable window when seat grabs
    are reset (#7669)
  * b0fca6ea input: kb focus mouse focused window if unset (#7666)
  * 4988e00b input: move idle notify to input handlers (#7659)
  * 0fad7a0b workspacerules: fix on-created-empty window focus (#7657)
  * 727f1b54 textinput: fix ime activation in some edge cases (#7660)
  * c80457be nix: add COMMITS var
  * 4a42c5ed config: Add a variable to prevent groups from merging after
    being dragged (#7650)
  * bd6d6e7f xwayland: add option to enable/disable xwayland (#7633)
  * 027140b7 sessionLock: ensure sls focus in some edge cases (#7647)
  * ea10592a input: don't emit idle activity when calling
    simulateMouseMovement (#7649)
  * 9b54342b Revert "syncobj: wait for deadline instead of available"
  * 8f9887b0 Nix: remove unused dependencies
  * fa39df47 CMake: drop unused deps after 016da234d0e8
  * f7249bd3 CMake: drop duplicate -luuid after 5262292abc56
  * 6934e7aa textinput: don't deactivate ime if another ti is focused
    (#7617)
